DESCRIPTION:Toronto Women in Business Networking Group (TWIB)\n\\*\\*You n
 eed to register on our website to attend this event and get the zoom link.
  RSVPing on Meetup does not mean that you are registered\, even though Mee
 tup.com will send you an email saying that you have. Thank you. Please go 
 here: https://gtapreneurs.com/networking-events-toronto\n\n\\*Please note 
 this event is advertised on multiple platforms\, and we expect around 20-2
 5 guests.\n\nDo you want more clients? Join us for GTApreneurs March 11-20
 26 Afternoon Virtual Business Networking Event to connect with other amazi
 ng entrepreneurs\, learn something new and promote your business!\n\nThis 
 event will feature Guest Speaker **Allan Pollett**\, SEO Guru & CEO\, Glob
 al Net Trade. Since 1998\, Allan has been working as a SEO and web marketi
 ng specialist. He is known as the "SEO Guru" having written several books 
 on reputation management\, social media and SEO related topics. Over the y
 ears\, he has helped over a 1000 businesses get to the top of the organic 
 search results. One of his most recent achievements is helping one of his 
 clients generate enough revenue from their YouTube channel to buy a Lambor
 ghini.\n\nLearn more about **Allan** here: www.AllanPollett.com\n\n**WARM-
 UP ITINERARY:**\n\n* **[11:45am-12pm: Pre-event networking]**\n* **12:00-1
 2:10pm:** GTApreneurs welcoming presentation\n* **12:10-12:30pm:** Guest S
 peaker Presentation: Allan Pollett\, ***"Get found = Get more clients: Is 
 it better to rank well in AI or in a Google search?"***\n* **12:30-1:00pm:
 ** Elevator Pitches (45 seconds each)\nFree\n\n**PREMIUM EVENT ITINERARY:*
 *\n\n* **[11:45am-12pm: Pre-event networking]**\n* **12:00-12:10pm:** GTAp
 reneurs welcoming presentation\n* **12:10-12:30pm:** Guest Speaker Present
 ation: Allan Pollett\, ***"Get found = Get more clients: Is it better to r
 ank well in AI or in a Google search?"***\n* **12:30-1:00pm:** Elevator Pi
 tches (45 seconds each)\n* **1:00-2:00pm:** Breakout rooms (Network 1-1 wi
 th other guests)\n\n**TICKETS**\n**GTApreneurs' Referral Group\, Exhibitor
  and Mega Networking Members:** Free\n**Non-members:** $10\n\\*Premium tic
 ket includes Guest Contact sheet emailed to you after the event. Note: You
  must attend the event to receive the guest contact sheet.\n\n**Event Orga
 nizer & Host:**\n**Tammy Defoe\,** President and Business Coach\, GTAprene
 urs\nVisit https://gtapreneurs.com/about and https://gtapreneurs.com/busin
 ess-coaching-toronto for more information about Tammy and her Business Coa
 ching and Consulting services.\n\n**QUESTIONS ABOUT THE EVENT?**\nContact 
