 VENUE:** Improve Canada\, 2nd floor auditorium\n**ADDRESS:** 7250 Keele St
 \, Vaughan\, ON (Between Steeles Ave W. and 407)\n\n**PARKING:** Free\, on
 site. Park on the NORTH SIDE of the building off of Snidercroft Rd\n\n**\\
