 head until you get to the main aisle. Straight ahead will be a staircase. 
 If you prefer to take the elevator\, make a right at the main aisle\, go d
 own a few stores and you will see it on the left.\n\n**EVENT ITINERARY:**\
 n\n* **5:00-6:00pm:** Open networking\, food buffet\, visit exhibitor boot
