 ral Group\, Exhibitor and Mega Networking Members:** Free\n* **Non-members
 :** $27 in advance or $29 on event day\n\n***Not a GTApreneurs Member?*** 
 Go here to view our memberships and register: https://gtapreneurs.com/busi
